Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:38.20,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}Brook's Past!\NThe Rumbar Pirates and Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:39.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Alright, close it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:43.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? What about Perona?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.69,0:02:46.45,Main,,0,0,0,,We looked, but we couldn't find her, so there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:51.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's fine now. Invisibility off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:57.90,Main,,0,0,0,,A magnificent escape, fosfos!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.90,0:03:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn, but my knees were shaking back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:06.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what "Tyrant Kuma" was doing on Thriller Bark...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, Absalom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:14.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Tyrant Kuma came to deliver the news about the successor of the former Warlord Crocodile. {Sewil: changed from "Tyrant Kuma came to deliver the news about the former Warlord, Crocodile's successor."}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.83,Main,,0,0,0,,His successor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.61,Main,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't the most important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:21.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Apparently, it's a guy called Blackbeard,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:24.36,Main,,0,0,0,,but what's really scary is what the guy's pulled off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:30.91,Main,,0,0,0,,The commander of the Second Division of the Whitebeard Pirates, Fire Fist Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:33.54,Main,,0,0,0,,...has been captured and taken to the great prison, Impel Down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:38.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Ace... he's famed as one of Whitebeard's best men...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The government's gotten themselves an incredible card...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:41.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:46.99,Main,,0,0,0,,They could easily try to use this to bring about the end of the Age of Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:53.17,Main,,0,0,0,,In this kind of situation, there's no time for Moriah-sama to just lie here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I understand what you're trying to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.13,Main,,0,0,0,,But I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:59.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Want a bride...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:01.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Right. Just get me a corpse that's your type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Not a zombie! I want a real, living woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.59,0:04:13.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Man, I guess we ended up all sleeping a whole day right out there in the courtyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:16.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, ya know, we did stay up that whole night fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:20.44,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(1000,0)}The day after Moriah's defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:18.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm hungry, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:20.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Go eat some cheese or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:26.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Cheese isn't good enough! I can't run on cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:30.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you take the cooking stuff over to the courtyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:34.46,Main,,0,0,0,,The Victims' Association guys don't want to leave the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:36.15,Main,,0,0,0,,so we're all gonna eat over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:40.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that! Everybody's so happy to finally be in the sun after all these years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.78,Main,,0,0,0,,They're all just lying there sunbathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:46.77,Main,,0,0,0,,But, how can you be in such a good shape anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:48.45,Main,,0,0,0,,It's totally strange. It's a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:50.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have enough ingredients?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.87,Main,,0,0,0,,We got back what was stolen from us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What's more, we even got a mountain of extra food, so we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.17,0:04:59.74,Main,,0,0,0,,But who brought that, I wonder... I guess there are some kind people here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.58,Main,,0,0,0,,They even brought all the treasure here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.58,0:05:06.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Even if this was Christmas, this really is too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:07.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:10.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, a glass bracelet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is cool! I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.69,0:05:19.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you can't just go around taking it like that, you know... R-Right, Nami-san...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.13,Main,,0,0,0,,It's fine. If it's just that one, it's not even all that valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:24.70,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:27.88,Main,,0,0,0,,However! I'm not giving you a single bit of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:32.31,Main,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna steal anything from the ship of our saviors, you know, Namizou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh! What a cool knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.16,Main,,0,0,0,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry! Oh, but it's got jewels in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? I just spoke without thinking... Who's Namizou?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, isn't it odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.42,Main,,0,0,0,,It kinda feels like I've seen you before somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:52.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:53.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Lola?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:56.27,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right... Did I even tell you my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,So it was you, Lola?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.03,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I got to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:02.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Lola, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa, hey! Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:06.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Could she really be that boar-zombie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:10.75,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't remember, huh? I'll tell you all about it later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll give you this! As a sign of my gratitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that alright? To me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:20.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Nami is giving treasure away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:24.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going on ahead, you think this will be enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.03,Main,,0,0,0,,A storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh, a storm? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.86,0:06:35.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is bliss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:38.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The light is... Hitting me, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.89,Main,,0,0,0,,We're still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.89,0:06:42.60,Main,,0,0,0,,We are...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.74,0:06:46.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:47.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:50.18,Main,,0,0,0,,We've brought food!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:54.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You should have asked us, we would've carried it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:56.17,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't have our saviours working like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:57.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Is Zoro awake yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:00.73,Main,,0,0,0,,He's still sleeping like a log... He's in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:03.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:07.01,Main,,0,0,0,,We've brought the stuff you asked for!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.01,0:07:08.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:10.21,Main,,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:14.39,Main,,0,0,0,,This is the first time Zoro's been this badly injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,He was really close to dying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:20.68,Main,,0,0,0,,I just know it... Something must have happened to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:22.89,Main,,0,0,0,,While we were unconscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:29.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Indeed. It's hard to believe that that man would just leave like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.53,0:07:32.33,Main,,0,0,0,,It's also weird that Luffy is so energetic all of a sudden, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I have no idea how that happened either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:39.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Actually, I saw it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:43.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw all of it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.51,0:07:44.91,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:46.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It's about what happened back then! {Halee: Added "It's" at the beginning of the sentence so that it doesn't sound too weird when connected to the previous one.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Come. {Sewil: changed from "Hey." as he says "koi" not "oi"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:51.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:54.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait, why? You were pretty cool too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:57.52,Main,,0,0,0,,"Take my life instead of the swordsman's", you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:08:00.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Hurry up and tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:06.45,Main,,0,0,0,,After I fainted, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:13.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, that Warlord had another crazy power, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:16.50,Main,,0,0,0,,He just put his paw on Straw Hat,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:19.14,Main,,0,0,0,,and repelled all of the damage that had been inflicted on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:21.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Damage...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Like a huge ball of agony!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:34.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Just touching a tiny bit of it, that swordsman screamed in pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:39.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I seriously thought that swordsman was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:41.02,Main,,0,0,0,,So, we actually cried!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.29,Main,,0,0,0,,We cried a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... Then, that's why Luffy is in perfect shape, while Zoro ended up like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:50.26,Main,,0,0,0,,How reckless...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:54.20,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Nothing... happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:59.88,Main,,0,0,0,,All right! We've gotta tell the rest of the crew this beautiful tale-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:03.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't you go running your mouths off with that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:06.49,Main,,0,0,0,,He didn't risk his life so that we'd praise him about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:07.80,Main,,0,0,0,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:12.80,Main,,0,0,0,,How do you think Luffy would feel if he knew all that pain he took on himself had gone and hurt his friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:17.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Just don't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:21.84,Main,,0,0,0,,As long as everyone is safe, that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm gonna go eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,T-T-T-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,They're super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:34.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What a lucky captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:38.02,Main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:44.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:48.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You said you knew something earlier, right?\NWhat did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't go askin' us that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone's safe... that's all that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I want to say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:03.25,Main,,0,0,0,,T-The beautiful tale of what a man had to endure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.77,Main,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never eaten anything so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:22.60,Main,,0,0,0,,We haven't eaten a proper meal in years! {Sewil: changed "for years" to "in years"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I've made plenty!\NDon't go leaving leftovers, you hear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:34.69,Main,,0,0,0,,I am so glad I got to eat your food again, Cook-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:37.97,Main,,0,0,0,,It is so good, I could continue until my stomach burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though I do not have a stomach!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.64,Main,,0,0,0,,You! Shut up and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.82,Main,,0,0,0,,What a funny skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:51.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Indeed, ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Being able to eat to my heart's content yesterday, and again today... I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:10:59.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I might be getting fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:02.20,Main,,0,0,0,,"Even if I'm just bones!", right?! Shut up, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Skeleton, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, how can you move, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:22.86,Main,,0,0,0,,We didn't even toast, but it turned into a party anyway, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:27.90,Main,,0,0,0,,He's not waking up even with this much noise... {Halee: Was "Even if it's this noisy, he's still not waking up..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.90,0:11:30.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Even though he's usually the toughest one here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:33.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chopper! This...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:35.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:36.80,Main,,0,0,0,,...is Zoro's share!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:39.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't make him drink that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:43.71,Main,,0,0,0,,What's with you?! Zoro likes this stuff, so it should make him better, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What kind of medicine is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:47.76,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:49.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, how about meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:52.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay! Thanks for the sentiment, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Just the sentiment, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:01.33,Main,,0,0,0,,There was a piano in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.22,0:12:08.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, weren't you a violinist?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:12.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I can play any instrument you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:18.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Um, about that conversation earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.49,Main,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I saw it all, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:27.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I was deeply touched by what the two of you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.86,Main,,0,0,0,,It sure is nice to have friends, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.61,0:12:36.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't bother saying "the two of you"... I just ended up looking like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:40.26,Main,,0,0,0,,No, you were just as prepared as he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:44.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Is there any song you'd like to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:45.94,Main,,0,0,0,,If you have a request...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:48.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Anything goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:50.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, how about...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:54.29,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yo-hohoho, Yohohohoo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:58.46,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yo-hohoho, Yohohohoo,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.42,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened to asking for requests?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:02.92,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Going to deliver Binks' Sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:07.32,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Following the sea breeze! Riding on the waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,"Binks' Sake"... I think I know this song from somewhere... It's very nostalgic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:31.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook! I know this song!\NShanks and his crew used to sing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.99,0:13:36.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Back in the old days, every pirate would sing this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Through hard times, and fun times...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Say, you're gonna come with us... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:49.61,Main,,0,0,0,,You got your shadow back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,So even though the sun rises, you can still travel, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:58.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Speaking of that... there is one thing I did not tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:13:59.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.68,0:14:04.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I have... a promise I made with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:07.14,Main,,0,0,0,,First, I have to fulfill that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:12.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Otherwise... I could not call myself a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:18.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Laboon, right? I know. Franky told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:23.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Laboon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:26.51,Main,,0,0,0,,That is indeed the name of that whale...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.86,Main,,0,0,0,,He is waiting for me at that cape...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Like I was trying to say, Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:33.38,Main,,0,0,0,,We met Laboon at the twin capes! It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:41.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I already know that Laboon has been waiting for his friends to return there for fifty years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, skeleton! What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:48.30,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not playing the piano as quickly anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It was a real surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:07.50,Main,,0,0,0,,We never thought that the last surviving one of the pirates he was waiting for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:09.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Would actually turn out to be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:16.62,Main,,0,0,0,,And... You still remember the promise, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Once he finds out, I'm sure Laboon will be really happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:25.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait... Wait a minute, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:29.14,Main,,0,0,0,,What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:34.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Out of the blue... are you telling me you really... met Laboon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.23,0:15:35.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.77,0:15:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Even after fifty years has passed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.31,0:15:43.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Laboon is still waiting at that cape, even now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.88,Main,,0,0,0,,We can vouch for it too! We really met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.40,Main,,0,0,0,,How was he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.79,Main,,0,0,0,,He was doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.17,Main,,0,0,0,,He was big as a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:16:01.51,Main,,0,0,0,,That I must see... back when we left him behind, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,He was still only the size of a small boat... He was rather cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.86,Main,,0,0,0,,He could be a little difficult sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:10.57,Main,,0,0,0,,but he loved music... he was a good kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.55,0:16:14.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Even now... If I close my eyes, I can see his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:17.87,Main,,0,0,0,,He is still there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:25.55,Main,,0,0,0,,So, that's how it is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.43,Main,,0,0,0,,So, he is still fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I have never been so happy before...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.38,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,What's with this whale? He's following the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:53.72,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Must've got separated from his herd, huh...? Poor little thing... The ocean's a big place...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:58.02,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,He looks so sad... And he's still just a kid, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, Captain Yorki... Shall we sing a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Brook! Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone, get your instruments!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.44,0:17:12.96,Main,,0,0,0,,We can bring a smile to even a crying child's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's show him what the Rumbar Pirates can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:15.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:18.46,Main,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:49.51,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hi, good day, everyone! It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:48.63,Captions,,0,70,200,,{\fad(200,200)}Rumbar Pirates\NMusician, swordsman
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:51.85,Captions,,0,70,200,,{\fad(200,0)}Brook\N(50 years ago, 38 years old)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us start singing our morning song!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:02.46,Main,,0,0,0,,And the power-tune we will be bringing you this week is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:05.74,Main,,0,0,0,,That famous song,\N"Black Handkerchief of Happiness"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.74,0:18:08.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone, feel free to join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:11.57,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, white handkerchief
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.18,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Don't let him find you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:15.61,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Run away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:19.16,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, white handkerchief
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.16,0:18:20.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Don't let the octopus get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:25.19,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Watch out for the ink! Look, there's a squid as well! That's the ink again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:31.06,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, white handkerchief
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:36.23,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,It's the all inked Black Handkerchief of Happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:26.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}P-Please stop making that noise so early in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:28.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We're getting up! We're getting up, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:31.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ugh, we're awake! We're awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:43.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook! Try playing that song as a ballad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Understood! The captain's favorite song!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,It's the whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:01.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey... you're that little guy from yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:04.58,Main,,0,0,0,,You still hanging around? Go look for your pod!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, how long is he going to keep following us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.66,0:19:14.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure his mom is worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.74,0:19:17.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Here, have some food, Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:20.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, since when does the thing have a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:28.45,Main,,0,0,0,,We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:43.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Help us! This guy has got a damaged leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Captain! An injured man fell into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:48.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Just throw out the life buoy!\NWe'll have to help him afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I suppose that is all I can do, seeing how I can not swim...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.02,Main,,0,0,0,,You saved us, Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! We're fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:01.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:09.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Alright, everyone sing! We're singing "that song"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.18,0:20:15.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You must be freezing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Treasure! We found it, Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:24.44,Main,,0,0,0,,We're gonna have a real feast today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:26.28,Main,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:34.75,Main,,0,0,0,,A sea monster appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Protect Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:53.36,Main,,0,0,0,,He likes you most, doesn't he, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.00,0:20:57.24,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, Laboon loves music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.24,0:21:00.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's probably because your heads have the same shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.54,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.99,0:21:23.36,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,You... can't you do anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.78,Main,,0,0,0,,We've all tried telling him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.73,0:21:29.85,Main,,0,0,0,,He won't listen to us, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:33.14,Main,,0,0,0,,You understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.41,0:21:38.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think we're strong enough to protect him if we take him any further...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,He's just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:46.46,Main,,0,0,0,,We can't take him with us to the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:57.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Please listen to what I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:22:01.50,Main,,0,0,0,,No, the song will have to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:05.30,Main,,0,0,0,,We certainly are comrades, but you are just a whale...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:09.38,Main,,0,0,0,,The Grand Line is a dangerous sea! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.38,0:22:11.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, you're a big kid now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.01,0:22:15.95,Main,,0,0,0,,but there are beasts out there like nothing we've ever seen here in West Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.95,0:22:17.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Laboon, listen to...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.52,0:22:22.18,Main,,0,0,0,,No use. He refuses to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:23.85,Main,,0,0,0,,It didn't work, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Then how about a song first?\NLet's sing that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.22,0:22:29.18,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,That would only make it worse, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.37,0:22:46.88,Main,,0,0,0,,This is no good... I know it's hard,\Nbut we've gotta turn our backs on him, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:51.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Until Laboon leaves the ship, we're not gonna sing or play any music.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.83,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be thrown overboard at this rate, captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.54,0:23:17.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Look at that! That's our guidelight, pointing to the entrance of the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.41,0:23:21.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Can anyone see Laboon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.55,0:23:24.75,Main,,0,0,0,,No, we haven't seen him for a week!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:28.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for him, but this was for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.83,0:23:31.80,Main,,0,0,0,,If he's lucky, he might be able to return to his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.73,0:23:37.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Men, are you prepared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:40.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We're ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:44.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Then let's go! To the world's largest ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:46.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.25,0:24:03.42,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm the lighthouse-keeper, Crocus. Good job making it over Reverse Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:05.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Welcome to the Pirate Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.49,0:24:09.29,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(700,0)}Grand Line Entrance\NTwin Capes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.92,0:24:09.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, hey, this isn't some kind of show, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:13.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Back in West Blue, I'm known as "Calico Yorki".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.06,0:24:17.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you, Crocus-san, but...\NWell, our ship got pretty damn beat up back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,You may stay as long as you wish, but I'll ask you\Nto help with the food and drinks while you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.38,0:24:26.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Man, you're something! Sponging off pirates, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.51,0:24:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Sure, sounds fair. Why don't you join us in our celebrations?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.29,0:24:32.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Today, we're all gonna throw a huge party!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.81,0:24:38.16,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, that whale that came with you, is that your pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.00,0:24:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.13,0:24:52.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.04,0:25:00.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook! Let's sing that song!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.24,0:25:02.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Captain, you really love that song, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.08,0:25:08.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's the song of pirates!\NLaboon! You love that song too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.42,0:25:14.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yohohoho, yohohoho
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.88,0:25:19.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yohohoho, yohohoho
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.47,0:25:27.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Going to deliver Binks' sake
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.50,0:25:31.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Following the sea breeze, riding on the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.84,0:25:35.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Far across the salty deeps, the merry evening sun
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.91,0:25:40.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Painting circles in the sky, birds singing along
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.38,0:25:44.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Farewell to the harbour, to my old hometown
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.69,0:25:48.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's all sing out with a DON, as the ship sets sail
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.95,0:25:31.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Crocus-san. Do you have a request?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.97,0:25:34.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Anything goes, huh, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.88,0:25:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Pirates love singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.00,0:25:51.09,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(150,0)}3 months later
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.04,0:25:56.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.24,0:26:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Laboon! Wait for us! Our ship is gonna sail straight ahead, and cross this sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.93,0:26:09.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It might sound strange, but we'll end up on the other side of the Red Line again...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.08,0:26:13.91,Main,,0,0,0,,And then we'll climb this wall once again, and return to this cape!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.91,0:26:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You just wait for that!\NIt should take about two or three years,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.36,0:26:20.72,Main,,0,0,0,,and after that, you'll see us all again!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.16,0:26:25.88,Main,,0,0,0,,When that time comes, you should have grown big and strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.20,0:26:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,See you later, Laboon! Stay well!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.32,0:26:36.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Laboon! When that time comes, no matter where we go, you can come with us on our adventures again!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.53,0:26:41.24,Main,,0,0,0,,We're comrades, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.44,0:26:52.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Laboon! We'll definitely travel around the world, and come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.24,0:26:54.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.44,0:26:57.24,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(150,150)}Three years later
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.27,0:26:59.86,Captions,,0,0,220,,{\fad(150,0)}The Florian Triangle
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.78,0:27:13.61,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook! Your techniques are incredible!\NCan you also teach me how to use a sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.55,0:27:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,A tornado?! But it was clear and sunny just a minute ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.52,0:27:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's run! Common sense won't work on this sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.67,0:27:53.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Man... now that we're actually here, this place really is unpredictable... Can we really hold up?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.77,0:28:00.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, but hey, a rough day just makes the sake at the end taste all the sweeter! Ain't that right, Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.68,0:28:03.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Play a tune for us again, today! Play that song!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.19,0:28:06.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew you would say that! Well then, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.94,0:28:09.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Do it, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.76,0:28:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,The mirror...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.60,0:28:23.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I see... So, I have become a skeleton...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.50,0:28:24.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.68,0:28:28.76,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Owowowowowow! That hurts, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.76,0:28:30.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Why am I getting punished too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.34,0:28:32.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Stop fighting about such stupid things!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.94,0:28:37.80,Main,,0,0,0,,But Captain, this guy nearly killed me with a stray bullet in that battle back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.80,0:28:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,But you're still alive, right? He's already apologized as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.00,0:28:44.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop fighting about stuff that's already in the past! It's pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.24,0:28:47.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.54,0:28:50.14,Main,,0,0,0,,That pain proves that you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.90,0:28:52.71,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.33,0:29:02.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Stars... This vast, starry sky... I wonder if Laboon is looking at it as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.31,0:29:05.48,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.48,0:29:09.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone, come and see this! Brook's being sentimental!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.29,0:29:13.10,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Please stop! That is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.29,0:29:18.50,Main,,0,0,0,,They're from the Navy Headquarters! What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.50,0:29:21.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be scared! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.20,0:29:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow, look! The captain's bounty just went up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.43,0:29:30.64,Main,,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.64,0:29:32.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us sing a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.93,0:29:39.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Yorki~! Yorki~! May his name echo all the way back to Twin Capes!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.24,0:30:06.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Terrible news! Hey, it's the captain! There's something wrong with Captain Yorki!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.59,0:30:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,An infectious disease?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.52,0:30:13.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.35,0:30:18.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Nobody go into the room... There are ten others infected besides the Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.90,0:30:23.53,Main,,0,0,0,,He may have got it in that jungle we passed through...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.90,0:30:27.24,Main,,0,0,0,,It's an undiscovered virus... I'm afraid there's nothing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.80,0:30:29.96,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a terrible situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.96,0:30:34.81,Main,,0,0,0,,If things go badly, it could kill this entire crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.28,0:30:40.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Captain... Captain Yorki...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.68,0:30:43.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't sound so damn depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.71,0:30:51.26,Main,,0,0,0,,You'll ruin the good name of the Rumbar Pirates, who can make a crying child laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.26,0:30:55.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll just be... leaving the Grand Line a little ahead of you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.64,0:31:02.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You guys just leave this old ship with us and the virus...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.22,0:31:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,You should... find yourselves a new ship, and keep on going!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.21,0:31:07.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.04,0:31:16.90,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll do what we can... and see if we can somehow make it out of the Grand Line through the Calm Belt...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.10,0:31:22.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it'll work out somehow. Sorry, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.13,0:31:24.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Give Laboon my best regards!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.80,0:31:29.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Wipe those looks off your faces, guys, and stand up straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.04,0:31:30.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.47,0:31:34.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.72,0:31:35.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.00,0:31:47.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't take it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.50,0:31:55.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Captain Yorki... I will never forget those words!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.47,0:32:02.87,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, Captain?! I have engraved them into my heart! Please... take good care of yourself... Captain!!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.27,0:32:09.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I shall be leaving this ship... But please... Live, and let us all meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.07,0:32:11.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Just take off this mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.61,0:32:14.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us all sing together again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.73,0:32:27.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.16,0:32:34.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Send me off with... My favorite song...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.44,0:32:52.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Going to deliver Binks' Sake...
